dct_title_s: The map of Peiping (Peking) : supplement to "Peiping shopping guide."
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines. Map of Beijing showing railways, buildings and places of interest. Map was published as supplement to: "Peiping shopping guide". The Map Library does not have a copy this book.
